name: Stargrail-Bearing Priestess
desc:
A priestess who offers requiem prayers to the celestial deity of the planet.
The staff she has obtained is a ritual tool handed down through generations, used to guard the people of the forest from the rule of the Jacknights by converting energy into barriers. Though she hides a mystical power within herself linking her to the forest's guardian dragon, she is usually a kind girl who treasures her childhood friend and older brother.
